To use DooFit externally, do the following:

1. Build DooFit
2. make install in your build directory of DooFit to install DooFit 
   (specify install location via -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/path/to/install
   at cmake call)
3. set DOOFITSYS environment variable to DooFit install location
4. set LD_LIBRARY_PATH or DYLD_LIBRARY_PATH (or whatever your system uses)
   to $DOOFITSYS/lib
5. build this project
